data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Located in a gated community, this move-in ready home features an open floorplan with 5 bedrooms + Den + large Loft, 3.5 bathrooms, and a 3 car garage.  Some of the many features include a covered lanai with a screened patio extension with pavers that was added in 2018, hurricane shutters, new water heater 2023, water softener, surround sound speaker prewire in living area & lanai, 5.25” baseboards throughout, and so much more!  Enjoy cooking & entertaining in your spacious kitchen that boasts a huge center island, walk-in pantry, stainless steel appliances, granite counters, hidden trash drawer, tilt out sponge tray, tile backsplash, pendant lights, and a large dining area.  The kitchen overlooks the great room with a soaring 21’ ceiling!  The sliding glass doors lead to the covered lanai and screened patio overlooking the back yard.  The primary bedroom is located downstairs with an extended seating area overlooking the back yard.  The attached primary bath has a walk-in shower with glass enclosure, relaxing garden tub, vanity with a granite countertop and dual under-mount sinks, linen closet, and a separate water closet.  The walk-in closet has custom built-in shelving, motion sensor light, and can be accessed from the primary bathroom as well as the laundry room!  The laundry room has a side-by-side washer & dryer, sink, and leads to the mud room/drop zone area.  The Den/Office can also be used as a formal dining room and has French doors, tray ceiling with crown molding, and wood floors.  There is storage closet under the stairs and a powder bath conveniently located on the 1st floor.  The secondary bedrooms are spacious and the huge loft area upstairs can be used as movie/media room, playroom, game room, or yoga/fitness area…the options are endless!  NO CDD fees & Low HOA fees- only $125/month.  There is a community playground and located nearby is the Bell Creek Nature Preserve with hiking trails and picnic tables.  A termite bond is paid through May 2024 and is transferrable to the Buyer(s) at Buyer(s) expense after closing.  Sellers are offering a 1 year home warranty up to $600.
